00e2y ngay nh\u00e9<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Meo_choi_da_3_ho_nghi_may_ngay_duoc_hieu_la_gi\"><\/span><b>M\u1eb9o ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p v\u1eebng g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y th\u00ec g\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e1 ba h\u1ed3. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u1ed7i h\u1ed3 kho\u1ea3ng 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 9 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u00fap g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m khi chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3193\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3193\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3193 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-6.jpg\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3i ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-6.jpg?v=1709303484 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-6-300x150.jpg?v=1709303484 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-4-6-768x384.jpg?v=1709303484 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3193\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3i ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <\/b>v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00ec g\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eebng ho\u1eb7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i g\u00e0 kh\u00e1c. Trong c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 th\u00ec g\u00e0 s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 ch\u1ea1y l\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe v\u00e0 t\u00ednh d\u1ebbo dai. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, g\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u0169ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. Ho\u1eb7c thu\u1ed1c theo ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn t\u1eeb b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3191\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3191\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3191 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-10.jpg\" alt=\"\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-10.jpg?v=1709303482 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-10-300x150.jpg?v=1709303482 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-2-10-768x384.jpg?v=1709303482 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3191\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u00c1p d\u1ee5ng g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ich_khi_cho_ga_choi_da_3_ho_nghi_may_ngay\"><\/span><b>L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi cho g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p <strong>g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 ba h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y<\/strong> s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c cho<\/span><b> g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">s\u1ebd gi\u00fap g\u00e0 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u1ee9c \u0103n. V\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p, gi\u00fap g\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n, t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd gi\u00fap g\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c m\u00f4 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a x\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1edbp do v\u1eebng g\u00e0. G\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y <\/b>c\u00f2n gi\u00fap g\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00edch t\u1ee5 \u1edf trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. Qua \u0111\u00f3, g\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 thanh l\u1ecdc m\u00e1u c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng th\u1eadn gan v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">G\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i c\u00f2n gi\u00fap g\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n. T\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ham chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ra \u0111\u00f2n chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi g\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n gi\u00fap g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao. Kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c g\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u00fap g\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, b\u00f9n, s\u00e2n c\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap g\u00e0 t\u0103ng tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3192\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3192\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3192 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-10.jpg\" alt=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-10.jpg?v=1709303483 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-10-300x150.jpg?v=1709303483 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-3-10-768x384.jpg?v=1709303483 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3192\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_nuoi_ga_choi_da_3_ho_nghi_may_ngay_chuan_xac\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i <strong>g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y<\/strong> hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, anh em c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn g\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u00f2ng d\u00f5i t\u1ed1t ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 k\u1ebf th\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb cha m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y ch\u0103m g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. C\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng cho g\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee9c \u0103n nu\u00f4i g\u00e0, n\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 giun, l\u01b0\u01a1n, rau xanh, \u2026 Qua \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u00edch t\u1ee5 m\u1ee1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00e3y ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp cho g\u00e0 theo h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y. N\u00ean cho g\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u00e1c g\u00e0 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng ho\u1eb7c kh\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean cho g\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y l\u1ed3ng. Sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn t\u1eadp th\u1eed, h\u00e3y lay v\u1ed7 v\u00e0 lau \u0111\u1eddm cho g\u00e0 r\u1ed3i. R\u1ed3i cho g\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 9 ng\u00e0y v\u1eabn quay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3 c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00e1 g\u00e0. N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh th\u00ec ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 cho g\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a g\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u00ec cho \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00e2n c\u00e1t, c\u1ecf. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xoay v\u00e0 nh\u1ea3y m\u1ea1nh th\u00ec ch\u1ecdn s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c s\u00e2n b\u00f9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3190\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3190\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3190 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-10.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-10.jpg?v=1709303482 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-10-300x150.jpg?v=1709303482 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/hinh-1-10-768x384.jpg?v=1709303482 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3190\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>G\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p v\u1ea7n g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u anh em nu\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn k\u00ea \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch mang l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1edbt t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u2026 Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn, g\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0, ki\u1ec3m tra s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y. Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a SV368 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. H\u00e3y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ngay v\u1edbi g\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eb9o g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi \u0111\u00e1 3 h\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0 \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Vi\u1ec7c cho g\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u1eady ngh\u1ec9 bao nhi\u00eau ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3192,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2478","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-da-ga"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2478","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2478"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2478\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5837,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2478\/revisions\/5837"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3192"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\